---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Early Childhood">
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface-sand relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white border border-surface-mist text-xs font-semibold text-brand-navy uppercase tracking-wide mb-6">
        Ages 2 months - 4 years
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Early Childhood</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-slate max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A warm, nurturing environment where your child can learn, play, and build a strong foundation for the future.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:text-brand-navy max-w-none text-text-ink leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Our Early Childhood program is designed to provide the highest quality care and educational opportunities for children aged 2 months to 4 years. We understand that these early years are critical for development, which is why our experienced teachers create a safe, engaging atmosphere tailored to each child's needs.
        </p>

        <h2>Program Details</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Ages Served:</strong> 2 months through 4 years</li>
          <li><strong>Hours of Operation:</strong> Monday – Friday, 7:00am – 6:00pm</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Locations</h2>
        <p>Our Early Childhood programs are conveniently housed within the following locations:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Plymouth Church</strong> (Milwaukee)</li>
          <li><strong>Lydell Community Center</strong> (Whitefish Bay)</li>
          <li><strong>Indian Hill School</strong> (River Hills)</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-surface-sand rounded-2xl border border-surface-mist flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <h3 class="mt-0">Ready to join the Milestones family?</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">Explore our enrollment process and secure your child's spot today.</p>
          <a href="/parents/enrollment" class="btn-primary no-underline text-white">View Enrollment Info</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
